{"tid":2317070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"好鄰舍北區教會稱戶口被凍結 滙豐暗指是按黑警要求凍結相關款項","createTime":"2020-12-08T09:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:47:19.000Z","uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"730c1692dff312df4b44378d4552d6a1ff596fd9","tid":2317070,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:58:30.000Z","msg":"好鄰舍北區教會又表示，教會於2016年註冊成為政府認可的免稅慈善團體，當中所有資金皆由香港各階層有心人及教會會友捐贈，一分一毫均為合法捐款；而教會亦於北區、元朗及觀塘提供30個免費宿位，至今服務超過70位無家者，是次凍結會令無家者住宿服務即時終止。教會嚴正要求滙豐立即解凍相關戶口，並為凍結行動提供合理解釋。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人回應表示，不能評論相關賬戶的事宜，無論在哪個市場營運，都必須符合當地的法律法規，<span class=\"red\">有關個案的情況請向相關執法機構查詢。</span>"},{"pid":"103bec3f4fcb5dfca8329d683264b544afe4e2cc","tid":2317070,"uid":108560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da409aaaa48b0546c0ffde72ac7cf58c467fbb6","tid":2317070,"uid":79117,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c6f9c63d4be488eb6050b1775a2e425233e068e","tid":2317070,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"琴日唔識咁講 唔屌都唔醒目"},{"pid":"13515fa43ea9e716d1f35692e87de73b39045578","tid":2317070,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e56c275d38a17ad99e6c3f3d0df2549b9142b4","tid":2317070,"uid":98431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"執撚左佢啦.jpg"},{"pid":"6bd6b6470eee06e3c90f51ff80926903f56a5ea1","tid":2317070,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit